{"tid":1958351,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個時勢竟然仲有班人搞黃色市集","createTime":"2020-04-04T14:38:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T03:49:20.000Z","uid":202321,"like":10,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1ce84996c9d61a1c0263d9f1b1df20c2b1c25b7e","tid":1958351,"uid":202321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T14:38:45.000Z","msg":"而呢班人就係我地stopday_zi<br />\n我地搞個市集個原本理念好簡單 - 經過年宵後黃色市集已經停咗，唔想黃色經濟在市集上就此完結，甚至希望每次都邀請到嘉賓上嚟發表一些關於黃色的想法。<br />\n<br />\n我地呢班連市集檔都未參與過嘅人便係3月頭膽粗粗咁去碼，勉強咁完成咗第一次，始終係因為新手和疫情初期，當中都受到一啲不能道出嘅苦況，甚至說不夠黃。<br />\n亦慶幸得到好多人嘅幫忙，先可以完成第一次個市集。（再一次對每一位幫助或參與過我們市集的人說一聲，多謝）<br />\n<br />\n現在我地將舉辦第二次市集及進行招募，並決定在5月29~5月31日舉行。<br />\n希望大家不要介意在31號這種日子舉辦，因為原本個日子想訂在5月頭，無奈疫情正大爆發當中，所以推遲到5月尾進行，而且6月正正是場運動一週年，我地團體對於自己和政府已經不敢作任何奢望，想在此之前爭取舉辦多一次。<br />\n<br />\nIG : stopday_zi<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EwP7WVD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEwP7WVD.jpg&h=9d5e3ad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下是我們的第二輪招募檔主計劃<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於我地團隊成日係到諗，點先可以再發展落去再幫到更多手足呢，所以我地決定咗搞一個一人一票投選你最愛的黃色檔主，而最受歡迎的兩檔會獲得各$300光時coupon，今次的租金會比上一次平咗之餘，我哋希望各位檔主可以將所得的收益捐比手足，希望同大家齊上齊落！<br />\n<br />\n日期：2020年5月 29-31日 （星期五至日）<br />\n時間：12:00am-10:00pm<br />\n地點：銅鑼灣駱克道波斯富街21-27號本德大廈2樓（娃娃星球2樓)<br />\n租金：1000+10%營業額作慈善（612或北區好鄰舍或香港獨立媒體）<br />\n截止日期：2020年4月19日（11:59pm)<br />\n報名表格 ：<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdX8P_V55W2z2-8Fmd-VWVMUcjbgMeyMO3qb3asf8PavjwHSA/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdX8P_V55W2z2-8Fmd-VWVMUcjbgMeyMO3qb3asf8PavjwHSA%2Fviewform&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=1867e7bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdX8P_V55W2z2-8Fmd-VWVMUcjbgMeyMO3qb3asf8PavjwHSA/viewform</a>"},{"pid":"909bc0273c73ae59d7c078541ae775a1314f05bd","tid":1958351,"uid":302,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T14:39:42.000Z","msg":"正式發起《我係黃店》運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1957985\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1957985</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BxW6rtF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBxW6rtF.png&h=503e1eb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n慢慢變黃又得 立即變黃亦得 得左<br />\n我係黃店 冇得彈"},{"pid":"ef9ac62ce160351c2c0b84cc247e125cc04bad3d","tid":1958351,"uid":49196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T14:47:41.000Z","msg":"以為樓主又想屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2afe2467691cc20d48f38bb9cf810078f6ce145","tid":1958351,"uid":353200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T14:48:16.000Z","msg":"麻煩師兄借一借個位<br />\n可唔可以入一入嚟幫幫本土議員撇除選舉不利因素,避免立法會選舉時到時發生優先老人同限制點票人數情況<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1958192\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1958192</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5e19693e1e5de8c9f92fee765d0beccfaa61b5a0","tid":1958351,"uid":202321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T14:48:21.000Z","msg":"我地嘅Ig連結佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B-chjU5pSAY/?igshid=f39cclnyko9s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB-chjU5pSAY%2F%3Figshid%3Df39cclnyko9s&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD1tn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=2d428498\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB-chjU5pSAY%2F%3Figshid%3Df39cclnyko9s&h=7e427455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B-chjU5pSAY/?igshid=f39cclnyko9s</a>"},{"pid":"2fd7c9e6da4abeac3480d2397b84df0551bc5422","tid":1958351,"uid":202321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef9ac62ce160351c2c0b84cc247e125cc04bad3d","tid":1958351,"uid":49196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T14:47:41.000Z","msg":"以為樓主又想屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T15:19:27.000Z","msg":"我地畀人屌就有份<im