r />\n三月中大家都開始鬆懈，亦正係呢個時間外地個案傳入香港，令疫情爆發，所以現家街嘅人流下降同時令確診人數較上星期慢慢地少一點點"},{"pid":"6ae8dbae397285c994d106f0ca71f3463c4c1822","tid":1958351,"uid":202321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:32:46.000Z","msg":"我地希望黃色經濟圈唔係淨得食店可以生存，食店告急大家都好容易睇到，好容易去幫，單單淨係黃店IG食遊記都好多個，而且Follow 人數個個都唔少。<br />\n<br />\n但樓上店，格仔店，網上店卻好少人留意，有一些除了有捐款甚至參與罷工，卻無人為意，難道黃色經濟只係食店和手調飲品嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a047fc29db1299430d289d8a435e3ec02c78a399","tid":1958351,"uid":202321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T19:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"9f20ce6dd187b0c1e4e602f2f4af0f4a7a562045","tid":1958351,"uid":3063,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T19:34:19.000Z","msg":"為左賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e566a661f96f9460f921b59aa8fc6227fdfb032","tid":1958351,"uid":1411,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T19:34:44.000Z","msg":"依家搞個會有人流既野......真係唔係太明智<br />\n如果真係有&gt;2個人中<br />\n只會比對家講黃絲年宵群組咁講一世"},{"pid":"4c56eda679a05de0d8ca3f1aad4d46d1e1c7e98a","tid":1958351,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T19:35:46.000Z","msg":"黃藍是政見，抗疫是良知喎！<br />\n<br />\n如成班手足為咗撐你而中招，你過意得去咩？<br />\n<br />\n又唔係一定要實體當面買賣"}]}